Strategic planning regarding the development and use of biomass in France. It highlights the different categories that might be mobilised; sustainability criteria and good practice; an estimation of the amount of biomass that would be necessary to satisfy energy needs; the current legislative framework (national and European) regulating biomass energy; production and mobilisation targets; complementary measures necessary to reach the targets; an evaluation of import needs; modalities of monitoring and evaluation.
